Baskin &amp; Danell (2003), Blake et al. (1998), Crete &amp; Daigle (1999), Cronin et al. (2005), Geist (1998), Lincoln &amp; Tyler (1994), Loe et al. (2007), Miller (2003), Reimers et al. (2005), Roed (2005), Roed et al. (2008), Schaefer &amp; Mahoney (2001), Vors &amp; Boyce (2009), Williams &amp; 
<collectingCountry id="F31E7642FFDCFFDDF70EF857EF3EF800" box="[2245,2307,2016,2041]" name="Heard Island and McDonald Islands" pageId="25" pageNumber="432">Heard</collectingCountry>
(1986).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
